headline: IQVIA’s (NYSE:IQV) Q4 CY2025 Sales Top Estimates
summary: Clinical research company IQVIA (NYSE: IQV) reported Q4 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 10.3% year on year to $4.36 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $17.25 billion at the midpoint came in 1% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.42 per share was 0.7% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
